  <brief_title>The Contribution of Heels for Walking Quality Among Children With Muscular Dystrophy</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Alyn Pediatric &amp; Adolecent Rehabilitation Center</agency>
